-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Shared Docker Networks (Best Practice)
If using docker-compose, place both pgAdmin and Postgres on the same custom network. You can then use the service name (e.g., db) as the hostname in pgAdmin.
yaml

services:
  db:
    image: postgres
    networks:
      - my-network
  pgadmin:
    image: dpage/pgadmin4
    networks:
      - my-network
networks:
  my-network:
