Install task:

zahir@zahir-ubuntu22:/etc/docker$ curl -1sLf 'https://dl.cloudsmith.io/public/task/task/setup.deb.sh' | sudo -E bash

zahir@zahir-ubuntu22:/etc/docker$ sudo apt install task
-------------- Run task:
$ task
$ task start_infra
$ task stop_infra

